                <div class="tit_nav">
                    <span class="tit_l">您所在位置：</span><a href="/Home/Index">首页</a><b>></b><span>案例信息</span>
                </div>
                <div class="content_box">
                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/10177" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">PJMT-0166</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">226 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">博弈与共生：中化学城投白城盐碱地治理项目的风险管理突围</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Game and Symbiosis: Risk Management Breakthrough in China Chemical Urban Investment&#39;s Baicheng Saline-Alkali Land Remediation Project</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">陈建校，何征东，高辰昕，常春馨，易荣霞</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">长安大学</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中化学城市投资有限公司</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">建筑、建材业与房地产业</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">大型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">综合管理部门/总经理办公室</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">18 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">决策型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中化学城投；盐碱地治理；项目风险管理；全生命周期管理；竞合博弈</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Sinochem Urban Investment; saline-alkali land management; project risk management; life cycle management; co-opetition game</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">本案例是央企中化学城投在吉林白城盐碱地治理项目的风险管理探索与实践。基于开展盐碱地综合利用、保障国家粮食安全与助力乡村振兴战略初心，中化学城投积极参与吉林白城4万多亩盐碱地治理项目。然而，因遭遇财政评审大幅核减施工成本、新增耕地指标跨省交易严控、H公司套利违约、B公司分包责任规避及联合体成员机会主义行为等不确定因素，导致公司面临投资亏损、融资难度与成本激增、现金流濒临断裂、农民工集体讨薪、联合体信任危机等复杂连锁问题及多重风险挑战，处于多元利益主体竞合博弈下的进退两难困境。作为国有企业，应当选择“退出止损”还是“坚守转型”，以实现白城项目的风险管理突围？如何有效识别、评价、管控项目全生命周期风险？如何有效平衡经济、社会、生态效益与项目风险？是中化学城投项目管理者亟待解决的重要管理难题。案例揭示盐碱地治理是一项集技术、政策、法律、社会、文化等因素于一体的系统工程，需融会贯通项目风险管理经典模型、分析方法与中国情境，着力构建“风险识别-动态管控-价值共创”的本土化范式，为工商管理与工程管理领域培养“懂技术、善管理、能创新、有情怀”的新时代复合型管理人才提供实践样本。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">This case analyzes Sinochem Urban Investment’s (SUI) risk management in saline-alkali land management in Baicheng, Jilin, based on China’s food security and rural revitalization goals. Initial progress under a government-market partnership faltered as financial audit cuts, frozen interprovincial land quotas, contractor defaults, and consortium opportunism triggered investment losses, financial strain, payment defaults, and operational paralysis. As a state-owned enterprise, should we choose “out or in” to realize the risk management breakthrough of the Baicheng project? How to effectively identify, assess and control the risks of the project throughout its life cycle? How to effectively balance economic, social and environmental benefits with project risks? The case shows that saline-alkali land management is a systematic project integrating technology, policy, law, society, culture and other factors, and it is necessary to integrate the classical model of project risk management, analytical methods and the Chinese context, and focus on building a localized paradigm of “risk identification - dynamic control - value co-creation”, so as to provide practical examples for the field of business administration and engineering management to cultivate new-age complex management talents who “know technology, are good at management, can innovate and have feelings”.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">经营管理人员,本科生,硕士生,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">采编/一手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2025</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《项目管理》、《项目风险管理》、《工程项目风险管理》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">风险分解结构、全生命周期动态风险管理、风险共担机制、融资风险管理；企业的可持续发展理论，三重底线原则；利益相关者理论，不完全契约理论，竞合博弈等</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2025-12</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
